2 10 10 1 2 Special Abilities: Kel Dors begin the game with one rank in Knowledge (Education).  They still may not train Knowledge (education) above rank 2 during character creation.

Dark Vision: When making skill checks, Kel Dors remove up to 2 setback dice imposed due to darkness.

Atmospheric Requirement: Kel Dors must wear a specialized mask to breathe and see outside of their native atmosphere.  A Kel Dor character starts the game with an antitox breath mask and treats oxygen as a dangerous atmosphere with Rating 8.  However, Kel Dors may survive in vacuum for up to 5 minutes before suffering its effects.
